1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means FlowMason, including all source code, binaries, 
documentation, and any modifications or derivative works.

"Commercial Use" means any use of the Software:
  - In a business, commercial, or institutional environment
  - For generating revenue or providing services to third parties
  - In a multi-user or shared environment
  - On infrastructure accessible beyond localhost
  - For providing automation services to clients or customers
  - In any context where money is exchanged for access or services

"Personal Use" means use that meets ALL of the following conditions:
  - Runs locally on a personal device (localhost or 127.0.0.1)
  - Accessed only by a single individual user
  - Not accessible via public domain or external network
  - Not used to generate revenue or provide services to others
  - Not deployed in business or institutional infrastructure

