6. ATTRIBUTION REQUIREMENTS
================================================================================

If you deploy the Software outside localhost (with written permission and a 
commercial license), you MUST display clear attribution:

"Built using FlowMason — https://github.com/chavanashutosh/flowmason"

This attribution must be:
  - Visible and readable in the user interface
  - Included in the footer, about page, or similar prominent location
  - Not hidden, minimized, or obscured
  - Present in all deployments

Additionally:
  - The "FlowMason" branding and name cannot be removed or replaced
  - Original copyright notices must be preserved
  - The Software's identity must remain visible

