This restriction applies even if:
  - Implemented using different technologies
  - Given a different name or branding
  - Modified or adapted significantly

You MAY build:
  - Private internal workflows for Personal Use
  - Connectors or integrations to contribute back to FlowMason
  - Personal extensions or UI refinements
  - Improvements to FlowMason itself

However, you may NOT publish these independently as competing products.

